            "type": "text",
            "text": "The LTX-2.3 22B Distilled INT8 video API is designed for high-efficiency video processing, utilizing a distilled 22-billion parameter model quantized to INT8 to minimize latency and resource consumption. This guide offers actionable insights for experienced API teams aiming to leverage this API in production systems."
