          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The LTX-2.3 22B Distilled INT8 video API provides a streamlined interface for video analysis and generation tasks. The model undergoes distillation to retain core capabilities while reducing complexity, and INT8 quantization cuts memory usage by up to 75% compared to FP32, enabling faster inference on standard hardware. Key use cases include real-time video enhancement, content moderation, and automated tagging."
