          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "resolution",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " and "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "output_format",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". Implement error handling for HTTP 429 (rate limits) and 503 (model unavailability). Authentication requires Bearer tokens in headers, and responses include processed metadata and confidence scores."
