            "type": "text",
            "text": "Optimize performance by batching requests to reduce overhead, and monitor latency using built-in metrics endpoints. For scaling, deploy behind a load balancer and cache frequent queries with tools like Redis. Ensure robust logging for traceability, and test failover mechanisms to handle API downtime. Regularly update client libraries to incorporate efficiency improvements from model updates."
